unfix hot
unfix cold

# 3) directional growth: the upper half is now a supercooled liquid (below Tm)
#    and freezes onto the cold solid interface -- the front advances upward

unfix baro
fix baro all nph x 0 0 2 y 0 0 2 z 0 0 2 couple xy
fix th all langevin 890 890 0.1 4321
run 15000
